[0m[49m[39m  211, 211[0m:[39m[49m         L --> M[Clinician Decision\nAccept / Override]
[0m[49m[39m  212, 212[0m:[39m[49m         M --> N[TPS / Record & Verify\nAction Execution]
[0m[49m[39m  213, 213[0m:[39m[49m     end
[0m[49m[39m  214, 214[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[39m  215, 215[0m:[39m[49m     style D fill:#ff9,stroke:#333
